<i>noun</i>: 냉방 [냉ː방] <br>
<ul style="list-style-type:square">
<li><i>noun</i><br>
<dt>냉방 [냉ː방]</dt><br>
<dd>1. air-conditioning</dd><br>
<dd>기계를 사용하여 실내의 온도를 낮추는 일.</dd><br>
<dd>The process of lowering the indoor temperature using a machine.</dd><br>
<dd>2. cold room</dd><br>
<dd>따뜻하게 하지 않아 차게 된 방.</dd><br>
<dd>A room that has not been heated and thus gotten cold.</dd><br>
</li>
</ul>